name: Satoshi is Female SPV NFT 01 DAO
description:
We are buying the first Satoshi is Female NFT drop from artist Tierra Armstrong. Get your pro rata fractional piece of the pie!

A DAO will be created if we win the Metaverso auction to manage governance and determine how we may want to collectively benefit from the shared NFT ownership. Eventually all proceeds will be returned to the contributors.
payDisclosure: All fund (less gas fees) will be returned in the event that we do not win the first Satoshi is Female NFT. Overages will also be returned in the event that we have more contributors than is required to win the auction.
